The equipment that is removed when you invoke chaotic spawn can be reworn / rewielded; additionally higher levels of chaotic spawn open up new ring slots for the player

--

Respawning towards end of chaotic spawn effect appears more efficient than two or more separate spawns; this is done by using chaotic spawn again

--

Progress to further tentacles in chaotic spawn mode is believed to scale with difficulty / XP of monsters slain (?) but it is still common to use low-level mobs to achieve the same effect

