--

look trashcan
This is a large, iron trashcan.
You can drop items you don't need in it.
To drop something in it type:    toss <object>
Only things with a value below 20 can be dropped in it.
As a thanks for using it you will receive up to 5 coins for each item tossed.
This item is in excellent condition.
It looks light weight.

