--

The sailor chest saves your stuff over the reboots. If the item can't be saved it pops out from the sailor chest. If the room does not support saving, a warning message is given.
The sailor chest is locked with a 3 dial combination lock.
Supported commands:

  open/close sailor chest
  label sailor chest as <label>
       It can be used to label the sailor chest to make usage
       of multiple sailor chest's easier.
  setowner sailor chest to [clear/yourname]
	  Sets the owner of the chest to identify item's real owner
	  incase of theft. You must carry the chest for this to work.
  kickover sailor chest
       Knock it over and spill all the contents
  get sailor chest
       It can be taken when closed/unlocked, unbolted and empty.
  bolt/unbolt sailor chest
       Bolted chests can not be picked up.

  setkey sailor chest to <symbols>
	   Set new secret combination. The sailor chest must be open.
  turn sailor chest to <symbols>
        When the lock changes state it makes a nasty sound.
        Example: turn sailor chest to @ @ @

--

