--

Commands available to you:
  open   <what>                            - Opens the beehive.
  close  <what>                            - Closes the beehive.
  insert <what> to <where> slot <num>      - Inserts honeycomb to given slot.
  remove honeycomb from <where> slot <num> - Removes honeycomb from given slot.
  clean  <what>                            - Removes dead bees from the beehive.
  label  beehive as <label>                - Labels your beehive.
  beehive help                             - This help.

--

Moor [newbie]: close beehive
Moor [newbie]: Don't leave it open, keep it cleaned
Moor [newbie]: check the condition of the inserts
Moor [newbie]: go talk to sister Jennifer and buy needed supplies
Moor [newbie]: bees happen automatically if I remember correctly

