exp bonus pool
--------------
SHORT VERSION:
While you have an exp bonus pool, you are awarded more experience for doing the usual things. When it is depleted, you will get no bonus. 

LONG VERSION:
Here is a rough summary of the exp bonus pool which affects all players (with less than 300 million experience).

Your pool contains exp. Every time you gain some amount of experience, the same amount is reduced from the exp bonus pool. Part of the reduced exp is added to the exp gain. So, new players effectively get double exp, and people closer to 300 million worth will get a smaller bonus.

The exp bonus pool restores with time, up to a maximum of 900k. It is also possible to replenish the pool with taskpoints. For details on this, see 'help exp'.

