To join the Barbarian guild after having a lot of experience, go to Digga's, then Raven.

"In Raven jail, kill jailkeeper to get key.  Unlock cell, open cell, enter cell. This frees Groo, the son of the Barbarian Chieftain.  Groo will give you the Barbarian Ring of Friendship in thanks for his freedom."

--

After getting the ring, go south down the path and do "search bushes" at A Turn in the Path. One can enter. Then "show ring". Then find Bankha and "join".

--

"barbarian binfo <your username>" to see your own Barbarian reputation

--

Corpses have to be totally immolated to count towards Barbarian reputation

--

If your Barbarian reputation appears full then it's capped; cap is raised (+300) with each level and goes away entirely at guild level 20

